import sys

def solve():
    sys.stdin.readline()
    arr = sys.stdin.readline().rstrip('\n').split(' ')
    arr = [int(_) for _ in arr]
    if sorted(arr) == arr:
        print('NO')
    else:
        print('YES')
    return

T = int(T)
for i in range(T):
    solve()
